longBusinessSummary: Gapwaves AB (publ) designs, develops, manufactures, and delivers waveguide products in Sweden, rest of European Union, and internationally. It offers automotive radar antennas, flat panel antennas, 5G phased arrays antennas, flange adapters, and waveguide filters. The company was incorporated in 2011 and is headquartered in Gothenburg, Sweden.
